    "body" : "<p>Here a version that uses shuffle and streams</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;Direction&gt; letters = Arrays.asList(Direction.values());\nCollections.shuffle(letters);\nreturn letters.stream().findFirst().get();\n</code></pre>\n"
