    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This is probably the most concise way of achieving your goal.All you need to do is to call <code>Letter.getRandom()</code> and you will get a random enum letter.</p>\n\n<pre><code>public enum Letter {\n    A,\n    B,\n    C,\n    //...\n\n    public static Letter getRandom() {\n        return values()[(int) (Math.random() * values().length)];\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
