    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I guess that this single-line-return method is efficient enough to be used in such a simple job:</p>\n<pre><code>public enum Day {\n    SUNDAY,\n    MONDAY,\n    THURSDAY,\n    WEDNESDAY,\n    TUESDAY,\n    FRIDAY;\n\n    public static Day getRandom() {\n        return values()[(int) (Math.random() * values().length)];\n    }\n\n    public static void main(String[] args) {\n        System.out.println(Day.getRandom());\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
